Haidee Wright https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Haidee_Wright 0 Haidee Wright (13 January 1867 – 29 January 1943) as Ada Wright was a London born English character actress. She began acting in plays in 1878 when a small child. She came from a family of actors and had a long career in the UK and the US with much Broadway work with occasional parts in films. Her parents and many siblings were actors. One of her brothers was Huntley Wright. Haidee_Wright ( 13_January_1867 – 29_January_1943 ) as Ada_Wright was a_London born English_character_actress .
